about_me.des: I'm a creative, motivated and enthusiastic Automation Developer/QA Developer/software engineer/developer with years of experience in software development and software QA engineering.\<br\>I have working experience span entire software development cycle (from requirement analysis, design, coding, debugging, quality assurance to after-sale customer support.) in an agile environment.

projects.Pebble: Saplatform is a automated service for operations, it has asset management, project release, database access function, it can control mass servers.
projects.jalpc: Jalpc is a simple, beautiful and swift theme for Jekyll. It's pretty minimal, but leverages large type and drastic contrast to make a statement, on all devices.
projects.angularjs: It is a web font application written by Angularjs and deployed by Jekyll on github (gh-pages), the backend platform is Leancloud, you can use Parse as well.
